OL,3,CPolar bears face starvation risk in
OL,4,Clonger ice-free periods in Arctic
OL,6,FThe new study monitored 20 polar
OL,7,Fbears, in the western Hudson Bay
OL,8,Fregion of Canada.
OL,10,FIt showed they tried different
OL,11,Fstrategies to maintain energy reserves
OL,12,Fon land, including resting, scavenging
OL,13,Fand foraging, but almost all lost
OL,14,Fweight rapidly over several weeks in
OL,15,FAugust to September between 2019 and
OL,16,F2022.
