OL,3,CPolar bears face starvation risk in
OL,4,Clonger ice-free periods in Arctic
OL,6,FThey are now spending around 130 days
OL,7,Fon land near Hudson Bay, whereas they
OL,8,Fused to spend 100 to 110 days onshore
OL,9,Fin the area.
OL,11,FThe individual polar bears were
OL,12,Fweighed and assessed for their energy
OL,13,Fexpenditure before and after the study
OL,14,Fperiod and fitted with GPS tags and
OL,15,Fcameras.
