OL,6,FOnly one increased its weight, after
OL,7,Flikely finding a marine mammal such as
OL,8,Fa seal or beluga carcass on land, the
OL,9,Fresearchers said.
OL,11,FTwo female bears were predicted to
OL,12,Fstarve to death before the average
OL,13,FNovember 30 freeze-up of the Hudson
OL,14,FBay, the study found.
