OL,4,Clonger ice-free periods in Arctic
OL,6,FLead author Anthony Pagano, research
OL,7,Fwildlife biologist with the US
OL,8,FGeological Survey polar bear research
OL,9,Fprogramme, said: "With increased land
OL,10,Fuse, the expectation is that we'll
OL,11,Flikely see increases in starvation,
OL,12,Fparticularly with adolescents and
OL,13,Ffemales with cubs," he said.
